description:
Explore and navigate the world with confidence using Google Maps. Find the best routes with live traffic data and real-time GPS navigation for driving, walking, cycling and public transport. Discover over 250 million businesses and places – from restaurants and shops to everyday essentials – with photos, reviews and helpful information.

Navigate the world, the way that you want:
• Get to where you need to go with fuel-efficient route options
• Find the best route with real-time, turn-by-turn voice and on-screen navigation
• Save time with automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Catch the bus, train and ride-share effortlessly, with real-time updates
• Find bike or scooter rentals to get around more easily

Plan trips and experiences effortlessly:
• Preview an area before you go (e.g. parking, entrances) with Street View
• Use Immersive View to experience what landmarks, parks and routes look like, and even check the weather so that you can be ready in advance
• Create custom lists of your favourite saved places and share with others
• Order delivery and takeaway, make reservations and book hotels
• Don't get lost with offline maps in an area with bad signal
• Search for local places and things to do, and decide based on user reviews and photos

Discover and explore like a local:
• Explore with confidence knowing 500 million users contribute and keep the map up to date each year
• Avoid the crowds by seeing how busy a place is before you get there
• Use Lens in Maps to see walking directions overlaid on the real world
• Filter restaurants by cuisine, hours, price, rating and more
• Ask questions about a place, from dishes to parking, and get quick answers

Some features not available in all countries or cities
Navigation isn't intended to be used by oversized or emergency vehicles

Know what's ahead on the road with the help from other drivers. Waze is a live map that harnesses the local knowledge of tens of millions of drivers around the world. Drivers safely and confidently reach their everyday destinations thanks to Waze map’s GPS navigation, live traffic updates, real-time safety alerts (including roadworks, accidents, crashes, police, potholes and more) and accurate ETAs.


Make your next drive more predictable and stress-free:
• Get there faster with real-time directions, accurate ETAs and automatic rerouting based on live traffic, incidents and road closures
• Even if you know the way, avoid surprises on the road ahead with safety alerts for accidents, crashes, roadworks, objects on the road, potholes, speed bumps, sharp curves, bad weather, emergency vehicles, railway crossings and more
• Steer clear of tickets by knowing where police and red light and speed cameras are located
• Share what’s happening on the road with other drivers by reporting live incidents and hazards
• Stay informed of upcoming speed limit changes, and keep your speedometer in check
• Know which lane to be in with multi-lane guidance
• See toll pricing and choose to avoid tolls along your routes
• Add road passes and vignettes for HOV lanes and restricted traffic zones
• Find petrol/fuel stations and prices and EV charging stations along your route
• Locate car parks near your destination
• Use voice-guided turn-by-turn navigation from a variety of languages, local accents and your favourite celebrities
• Plan your next drive by checking ETAs by future departure or arrival times
• Use your favourite audio apps (for podcasts, music, news, audiobooks) directly within Waze
• Sync Waze to your car’s built-in display through Apple CarPlay


* Some features are not available in all countries


* Waze navigation is not intended for emergency or oversized vehicles


You can manage your in-app Waze privacy settings at any time. Learn more about the Waze privacy policy here, www.waze.com/legal/privacy.

GO TO-U is your personal EV companion, redefining the charging experience for electric vehicle drivers. With access to over 950,000 charging stations in 67 countries, we make charging your EV easy, reliable, and stress-free. Whether you’re cruising the highways of Europe, navigating vibrant cities in Asia, or embarking on a cross-country road trip in North America, GO TO-U connects you with top-tier networks like Tesla Superchargers, Ionity, GreenWay, EVBox, ChargePoint, Has·to·be, Allego, EVgo, and many more.

What sets GO TO-U apart is our Advanced Reservation Technology (ART) – a game-changing feature that allows you to reserve a charging station in advance. No more waiting in line or dealing with uncertainty. With ART, your charging spot is guaranteed, giving you the confidence and peace of mind to focus on your journey.

Our app is designed to simplify every step of the charging process. Use intelligent filters to find the perfect station based on operator, connector type, power output, or infrastructure. Our smart route planner goes beyond basic navigation by recommending charging stops tailored to your vehicle’s specs and current battery level, ensuring your trip is optimized from start to finish.

Stay in control with real-time session tracking, and access detailed summaries of your charging history with our "Charging Overview" feature. Payments are secure and effortless, whether you prefer using a credit card or the in-app wallet.

But GO TO-U is more than just a charging app – it’s a rewards platform too. Earn points for every charging session and redeem them for exclusive merchandise, discounts, or partner services. And with 24/7 customer support, help is always just a tap away, so you can drive with confidence, no matter where the road takes you.

GO TO-U combines innovation, simplicity, and reliability to transform the way you travel with your EV. Download GO TO-U today and experience a smarter, more convenient, and rewarding EV lifestyle. Let us power your car, your confidence, and your journey into the future.

Power your EV journey with ECOFACTOR, where over 300,000 EV drivers across Ukraine, Europe, and Central Asia connect to unlock seamless charging experiences. Find the perfect charging stations that match your route, your schedule, and your EV. ​

Our EV driver app offers a range of features designed to streamline the charging experience: sort by connector type and speed, check & leverage real-time data, reserve your charging spot in as little as 15 minutes in advance, pay with Apple Pay, Google Pay or credit/debit card, monitor charging session in real-time, and track your charging history along with expenses. ​

​Whether you're planning a short trip or a cross-country adventure, ECOFACTOR makes it easy to charge your EV anywhere along the way. Just pick your destination and we'll show you all the EV charging stations along your way, including real-time availability, charger type, and charging speeds. 

Why ECOFACTOR will become your EVerething you need to recharge: ​
1. ​ Find the nearest EV charging station by speed (7 kW, 9 kW, 22 kW, 50 kW) and connector type (ССS 1, CCS2, Type 1, Type 2 Plug, Type 2 Socket, CHAdeMO, GB/T DC, GB/T AC). ​
2.  Plan your EV journey in advance with the ability to map out charging stops and time your breaks efficiently. ​
3.  Check the real-time availability of charging stations along your route, so you never arrive to find a station full. ​
4.  Reserve your charging spot  in as little as 15 minutes in advance. ​
5.  Pay securely with Apple Pay, Google Pay, or your credit/debit card, without the need to carry cash. ​
6.  Check in advance if a connector of your choice is available at the charging station, ensuring there are no surprises during your stop. ​
7.  Start/stop your charging session remotely, giving you full control without leaving your car. ​
8.  Track your charging session in real time, with up-to-the-minute progress updates. ​
9.  Monitor your charging history and expenses, keeping you informed of your energy consumption and costs. ​
10. Access 24/7 support directly from the app, helping you resolve any issues quickly and easily. ​

Need help? Our customer service is available 24/7: https://ecofactor.ua/information

ECOFACTOR has been providing integrated EV charging solutions to Charge Point Operators (CPOs) for over 10 years. To date, we've manufactured 18,000 charging points used in 11 countries and developed our own Charge Point Management Platform for over 500 customers, including Amazon, Swiss Embassy in the UK, SOCAR, Megawatt, Yasno, and many more. ​

Join over 500 ECOFACTOR clients and become a Charge Point Operator. Grow your revenue with us – contact our sales team: ​info@ecofactor.ua

Need an EV charging station installed in your area? Let us know, and we'll add this to our to-do list.  ​

Follow us on social media to be the first to know about our new EV charging stations, app updates, and company news. 
https://www.facebook.com/ecofactor.ua
https://www.instagram.com/ecofactor.ua/

description:
TOKA Energy — це сучасний додаток для водіїв електромобілів, який забезпечує швидкий доступ до зарядних станцій для електромобілів та повний контроль над процесом заряджання. Наша мета — зробити використання електротранспорту максимально комфортним та ефективним. TOKA пропонує зручне рішення для тих, хто шукає електрозарядні станції в Україні або планує маршрути через зарядки для електромобілів.

Особливості додатка TOKA Energy

- Пошук зарядних станцій: Знаходьте найближчі станції зарядки електромобілів за допомогою інтерактивної карти зарядних станцій або плануйте маршрути із зупинками для зарядки авто.
- Реальний час: Перевіряйте статус зарядок електромобілів, доступність портів, типи конекторів та вартість зарядки прямо в додатку.
- Фільтри для вибору станцій: Обирайте зарядні станції відповідно до ваших потреб: тип конектора, потужність зарядки та інші параметри.
- Зручна оплата: Сплачуйте зарядку прямо в додатку. Підтримка Apple Pay, Google Pay та банківських карток гарантує безпеку та швидкість транзакцій. Використовуючи додаток для зарядки электромобиля, ви отримуєте доступ до всіх послуг Toka Network у кілька кліків.
- Аналіз витрат: Переглядайте історію зарядок авто із деталізацією за місцем, часом і витратами.
- Сповіщення: Отримуйте актуальні повідомлення про статус зарядки, доступність електрозарядок, новини та акційні пропозиції.
- Авторизація на станції: Починайте заряджання за кілька секунд завдяки авторизації через додаток.

Переваги TOKA Energy
- Широка мережа станцій: Доступ до зарядних станцій України у багатьох містах та регіонах.
- Зручність використання: Інтуїтивно зрозумілий інтерфейс додатку, що включає інтерактивну карту зарядних станцій.
- Ефективність: Дані в реальному часі дозволяють економити час і заряджати авто без затримок.
- Екологічність: Ми сприяємо розвитку екологічного транспорту для чистішого майбутнього.

TOKA зарядні станції — це не лише швидкість і надійність, але й сучасний підхід до розвитку електрозаправок України.

Як почати користуватися?
1 - Завантажте додаток. 
2 - Створіть профіль. Зареєструйтесь за допомогою електронної пошти або соціальних мереж.
3 - Додайте інформацію про автомобіль. Це допоможе отримувати персоналізовані рекомендації.
4 - Керуйте зарядкою. Шукайте зарядні станції, бронюйте порти, оплачуйте та контролюйте процес заряджання.

Про компанію TOKA
TOKA Energy — провідна компанія в Україні, яка розвиває інфраструктуру для електротранспорту. Ми прагнемо зробити електромобільність доступною, надійною та комфортною.

Завантажте TOKA Energy зараз і зробіть заряджання вашого електромобіля простішим, ніж будь-коли!

EVA Chargers gives you access to over 1000 charging stations.
Start charging in two taps. Control the process and get up-to-date information. Keep track of your expenses.

- For EV drivers 
Looking for the nearest charger or a specific connector?
Need to find a place to have dinner or spend the night and charge your electric car?
We have everything!
Just choose a place and manage the charging process.

Moovit is one app for all your urban mobility and transport rides!

Dailymail - "This travel app is a godsend for anyone using public transport – with live updates to bus schedules, as well as a great route-planner for cities across the UK."

Transportation is an integral part of urban living. Whether you ride the train, subway/underground /tube, bus, light rail, ferry or metro, use bikes, ride-sharing like Uber, getting the best urban mobility information is critical. Moovit guides you from point A to B in the easiest and most efficient way. Get train and bus times, maps, and live arrival times with ease so you can plan your trip with confidence. Find critical alerts and service disruptions for your favorite lines. Get step-by-step directions of optimal route bus, train, metro, bike or a combination of them. 
This is why Moovit has been named one of the best apps of the year 2017 by the App Store!

Moovit guides more than 865 million users in over 3200 cities throughout the world.

► Journey Planner that combines you all transport options and gives you the best route with live arrivals.

► Live Directions: Get step-by-step directions with live guidance as you travel: know exactly how long you need to walk to your station, how long you’re waiting, view the arrival time of your line and how many stops are left. 

► Real time arrivals. View real-time arrival updates, which are taken directly from GPS devices positioned on buses and trains.

► Real time alerts. Know about issues ahead of time by receiving service alerts such as emergency or unexpected disruptions, delays, traffic jams, new construction and more...

► Users reports. Moovit’s users report issues found with stations, line service, and timetables so that we can inform all nearby riders about what’s going on in their area.

► Favorite lines, stations, and places. Get easy access to lines, stations, and places you ride and visit all the time. Plus, get real-time updates if/when there are changes to your favorite lines in case your bus or train time is impacted!

► Bike routes. Get bike routes in addition to the bus, subway, train, or metro trip plans. If you ride bikes (yours or shared) we can plan a route that includes the train or bus. 
Bike docking stations are updated in real-time.

► Maps view. View all stations, routes, and lines on the subway or bus map. Additionally, maps are available in PDF for when you’re offline, or underground on the subway.

Download the most accurate EV and Tesla charging station map. 

PlugShare is the world’s largest EV driver community. Drivers contribute station reviews and photos to help the EV community make the most informed charging decisions possible. 

Drivers can filter the PlugShare map by plug type, including CHAdeMO and SAE/CCS, as well as charging speed, including Level 1, Level 2, and DC Fast Chargers such as Tesla Superchargers. You can also filter by charging provider – the PlugShare map includes detailed station information for every major EV charging network in North America, Europe, and much of the rest of the world, including:

- ChargePoint
- Tesla Destination
- Electrify America
- Supercharger
- EVgo
- FLO
- SemaConnect
- Shell Recharge
- Renovatio Asset Management
- Chargefox
- Blink
- SemaCharge
- Volta
- bp pulse
- BC Hydro EV
- GRIDSERVE Electric Highway
- ChargeNet
- Sun Country
- NRMA
- Petro-Canada
- Circuit Electrique
- Pod Point
- Evie Networks
- GeniePoint
- Vector
- Lidl eCharge
- Ivy
- Osprey Charging Network Ltd

With PlugShare, you can:

- Find public charging stations compatible with your EV (or EVs if you have multiple electric vehicles)
- Filter for connector type, charging speed, and amenities like food or bathrooms
- Check for station functionality and current availability 
- Link to your favorite navigation app for directions to your selected charger
- Pay for charging with Pay with PlugShare (at participating locations) and monitor your session
- Add new charging stations to the map as you discover them
- Receive notifications when a new charger is installed nearby
- Find all the charging stations along a road trip route with a built-in EV trip planner
- Use PlugShare with Apple CarPlay to browse nearby charging locations, bookmarked locations, and trips you've planned from the built-in display of CarPlay compatible vehicles
- And more! 

PlugShare helps drivers find chargers compatible with any EV, including Tesla Model X, Tesla Model Y, and Tesla Model 3; the Ford Mustang Mach-E, Chevrolet Bolt, VW ID.4, Nissan LEAF, BMW i3, Audi e-tron, Hyundai Kona, Hyundai Ioniq 5, Porsche Taycan, Kia e-Niro, Volvo XC40, Polestar and all other electric vehicles on the market. 

Download PlugShare and join the PlugShare community today!

ICW Connect is an application for paying for services at a self-service car wash. Download the application, get a free car wash when you first register and enjoy using a smart self-service car wash to make your car cleaner.

ICW Connect - helps you find a self-service car wash, get directions, pay for a few-touch car wash service.

To use you should:
- open ICW Connect application
- register with a phone number
- select a car wash on a city map, get directions
- scan the QR code located on the control panel in the free box of the car wash
- select the necessary amount to pay for car wash
- click «Pay», the money will be debited from your bank card tied to the application, the amount paid will be displayed on the digital display of the control panel.

Invite your friends to use the application, you and your friends get a bonus.
A list of your friends with the status of the installation of the application.
Your history of visiting ICW car washes and payments with a filter by date. Bonus accrual history.
Map of car wash self service and user comments.
Current promotions and discounts on car washes.

ICW Connect allows you to:
- Get a free car wash on the first registration of the application, on the balance of 50 bonuses
- Find the nearest ICW car wash on the map and get directions
- View rating and rate car wash
- See the history of payments and accrued bonuses
- View current promotions at a car wash
- Receive a CASHBACK after paying for a car wash
- Invite Friends to use ICW Connect, you and your friend receive a bonus after registration and the first wash.

Île-de-France Mobilités is here to assist you daily. Purchase a digital ticket, recharge your Navigo pass, search for routes including trains, RERs, metros, trams, buses, coaches, bicycles, Vélib', car-sharing, or car rentals. Find schedules in real-time or traffic information... Discover essential tools and information for organizing your travels in Île-de-France. Together, let's travel with ease.

Avoid queues at stations: buy your transport tickets from your iPhone!
The following tickets are available for purchase:

- Metro-Train tickets or Bus-Tram Ticket
- One Way from/to Airports (you cannot purchase this ticket if you already have a Metro-Train Ticket charged on your device)
- Navigo daily (this fare doesn’t permit you to go to airports), weekly, or monthly passes
- Special fares (Anti-pollution pass, Paris-Visit Passes etc.)
- Daily Vélib’ passes

Purchased tickets can then be (depending on the chosen purchasing path):

- Stored on the iPhone and validated directly at stations (from iPhone Xr and iOS 17.5)
- Loaded onto your Navigo pass (from an iPhone 7, with at least iOS 13. iPhone XR and XS are compatible starting from iOS 14.5)

For compatible tickets (Metro-Train and Bus-Tram Tickets, Navigo Day passes, special fares), no account is needed, and you can pay directly with Apple Pay!

You can prepare and plan your travels:

- Find nearby bus stops, train stations, and metro stations
- Search for real-time public transport routes, car-sharing, and bicycle routes
- Save upcoming trips in your phone’s calendar
- Check the next departures for your lines in real-time and all the timetable information
- View maps of public transport networks (accessible even offline)
- Follow pedestrian routes for walking segment

Stay informed and anticipate disruptions:

- Check your lines’ Twitter feed for real-time traffic updates
- Get alerts for disruptions on your favorite lines and routes
- Stay updated on the status of elevators in the stations you use

Customize your travel:

- Save your destinations (work, home, gym, etc.), stations, and stops as favorites
- Customize your profile (fast walker, with difficulties, reduced mobility, etc.)
- Select lines or stations to avoid

Prefer soft or alternative modes of transport:

- Book car-sharing and/or ride-sharing trips in partnership with leading providers
- Opt for bicycle routes for all your trips
- Rent a car or a van for a short period by choosing a Communauto car-sharing vehicle from a wide selection of stations around you and book it immediately for the duration of your choice.
--
Already using the Île-de-France Mobilités app and enjoying its services? Let us know with a 5-star rating!
Experiencing bugs or having feedback to give? Help us improve by sending your suggestions through the contact form available via the personal space.

Say hi to your co-driver.

You’re searching for a top-notch EV charging experience? Here you are: Download the IONITY App to access Europe’s leading High-Power Charging (HPC) network available across 24 countries – open to EVs from all manufacturers. Our network delivers maximum charging speeds of up to 400 kW, enabling you to charge 300 kilometres of range in 15 minutes. Faster charging sessions — more time for you. 

Discover the highlights of the IONITY App

Navigation
•	Search and find the nearest or a specific IONITY Station — the availability of all charging points is displayed in real-time.
•	Use the IONITY Route Planner to plan your journey ahead and import your daily or upcoming routes to your favourite navigation app with ease. 

Charging
•	Conveniently start and end your charging session directly within the IONITY App.
•	Track your charging progress in real-time and receive a push notification when you’re at 80% to go back on the road.
•	Optional: Use our app to scan the QR code on the charger to start the session. 

Payment
•	Safely store your account and payment details within the app to conveniently pay for your charging sessions.
•	Receive monthly invoices for your personal or professional use to keep an eye on your spendings.
•	Have a closer look at your past IONITY charging sessions and explore useful information like session duration, kWh charged and charging curves.

Find the right IONITY Subscription for you

Discover our subscriptions within the app: Choose the one that matches your lifestyle, driving habits, and charging needs by opting for IONITY Power or Motion. Sign up now and charge your electric vehicle at very attractive price per kWh. Prices vary by country. 

IONITY Power
Power your EV and charge for less: Our IONITY Power subscription is the right choice for most EV drivers. You save money after only two charging sessions per month: Benefit from the cheapest charging prices per kWh and continue your journey fast.

IONITY Motion
Keep yourself in motion: IONITY Motion is the ideal subscription for drivers that only occasionally use their electric vehicle and want to benefit from a cheaper charging price per kWh by using the IONITY App.

Your benefits with IONITY Power and IONITY Motion:
•	A significantly lower charging price per kWh
•	No seasonal or peak changes of kWh prices
•	Switch your current subscription anytime 
•	Cancel subscription anytime to next billing date
•	Subscribe and pay via the IONITY App

Charging for registered users without IONITY Power or Motion subscription:

IONITY Go
Ready. Set. Go! Sign up within the IONITY App and automatically benefit from a slightly lower charging price per kWh. No subscription and no monthly fees. This is IONITY Go. Upgrade to our subscriptions to save even more.

About IONITY
IONITY builds and operates Europe’s largest ultra-fast charging network. With a High-Power Charging (HPC) capacity of up to 400 kW, it enables maximum charging speeds. IONITY exclusively uses renewable energy, ensuring emission-free and carbon-neutral driving. Currently, the IONITY network includes over 700 charging stations and more than 4,800 HPC charging points across 24 European countries.

IONITY was founded in 2017 and is a joint venture between the car manufacturers BMW Group, Ford Motor Company, Hyundai Motor Group, Kia, Mercedes-Benz AG and Volkswagen Group with Audi and Porsche as well as BlackRock's Climate Infrastructure Platform as a financial investor. The company is headquartered in Munich, Germany, and has additional offices in Dortmund, Germany, the French metropolis Paris, and outside the Norwegian capital Oslo. Further information at www.ionity.eu.

Are you looking to rent or buy property?

The only app that combines real time alerts with the best offline radar detection alert system. With Radarbot, you will have the best radar alerts, real time traffic alerts and specific speed limit alerts for different vehicles (cars, motorbikes, trucks and commercial vehicles) in one powerful app. Focus on what really matters while driving and enjoy your journey.

With Radarbot, drive more peacefully. Safer. Better.

SPEED CAMERA WARNINGS
Enjoy driving without having to worry about risking your safety or driving licence. Avoid traffic fines and penalties by receiving clear warnings before passing speed cameras:

- Fixed speed cameras.
- Possible mobile speed cameras (frequent areas).
- Tunnel speed cameras.
- Average speed cameras (the app displays the average speed).
- Traffic light cameras.

Plus:
- Dangerous driving areas.
- Seat belt or cell phone use cameras.
- Restricted area access control cameras.
- Potholes and speed bumps on the road.

* FEATURES:
- Works in any country.
- Compatible with other apps. You can use Radarbot together with other GPS navigators or your favourite music app. You will still receive alerts in the background or while the screen is turned off.
- Alerts only in the direction you are driving. The app automatically ignores speed cameras for traffic going in the opposite direction or off route.
- Voice alerts.
- Sound alerts when approaching a speed camera or going over the speed limit.
- Vibration mode for motorists.
- Fully configurable warning distances and parameters.
- Automatic Bluetooth connection and startup.
- Compatible with Apple Watch.

REAL TIME ALERTS
Real time alerts will warn you of any unexpected circumstances. Radarbot has a community of over 50 million drivers worldwide with whom you can share and receive alerts. Find out immediately what is happening on the road and avoid traffic jams, hazards, accidents, mobile speed cameras, police, helicopters, drones, and much more.

SPEED CAMERA UPDATE
Radarbot has the most powerful, up-to-date speed camera database in the world. Our team of experts perform daily updates to ensure that the database always contains the very latest information. Not a single speed camera can escape the prying eyes of Radarbot!

RADARBOT WORLDWIDE
Try our totally "FREE" version for as long as you like. If you want to get the full experience, you can try "Radarbot GOLD" and "Radarbot GOLD RoadPro" with integrated GPS navigation, unique advantages and, of course, no advertising.

GPS NAVIGATION AND SPEED LIMITS
Discover the power of Radarbot. The GOLD version offers everything you need on the road in a single app: GPS navigation, speed cameras and speed limits. Even if you don't have an internet connection, you will still arrive safe and sound at your destination. Get speed camera alerts wherever you are in the world without having to worry about using up your mobile data.

Where would you like to go?

* FEATURES:
- Offline navigation and 3D maps.
- Possibility of choosing a route with fewer speed cameras.
- Road speed limits.
- Alerts for school areas and associated speed cameras.
- Radarbot co-pilot. Put your seat belt on!

ARE YOU A PROFESSIONAL DRIVER?
"Radarbot GOLD RoadPro" includes everything a professional driver could need:

- Routes with special restrictions for lorries and commercial vehicles.
- Speed limits and specific speed cameras for lorries.
- Distance alerts adapted to heavy vehicles.

If you have any doubts or queries, we would be more than happy for you to get in touch with us at radarbot@iteration-mobile.com or by using the customer support option inside the app.

Download Radarbot now and become a member of the "Enjoy driving!" movement.

Application M2M Local is mobile client that maintain access to Wialon Local GPS tracking platform anytime, anywhere. User-friendly interface allow to:

- Display information about monitoring objects in real time: location, tracks, sensors, etc.

- Display information about your own location on map with other objects, geofences and place of interests

- Controlling objects: share location, navigate to object with navigation app, send commands

- Tracking objects: displaying tracks on map, start/finish markers on map, displaying parameters each track (time, distance, max speed)

- Reports: generate the required report for the required object for the specified period of time and save it in PDF locally

- Status: all important information about your objects in one tab

The application supports the following languages: English, Ukrainian, Russian. 

Please note that:
- object names are not translated - they are displayed as the user created them in monitoring system.
- addresses are not translated - they are displayed on language of country where it located
- application M2M Local is mobile client, application do not collect information about your tracks or tracks of other object.
- all information with which the mobile client works is stored and processed in the monitoring system (exception - report in PDF format)
